# Assignment 3 - KPMG Customer Data Analysis

This project includes cleaning and analyzing customer, transaction, and address data to generate business insights using Excel.

## Key Objectives

- Clean missing values, remove duplicates, restructure data
- Analyze customer demographics and segments
- Track transaction trends and top products
- Use pivot tables and charts for visual insights

## Key Findings

- Highest CLV observed in telecom and entertainment sectors
- NSW has highest new customer influx
- Male customers lead in long-term value; females lead in recent revenue
- May, August, and October show peak sales months

## Recommendations

- Launch targeted campaigns for high-CLV customers
- Expand in high-growth regions (NSW, QLD, VIC)
- Introduce subscription options for repeat buyers
